==================
=  Description:  =
==================
Hangman game.
The purpose of the game is to find a word among a dictionary, by choosing 
letters that suppose compose the word.
Add: the payer can ask to a hint

All functions that i used:

- update_word_pattern(word, pattern, user_letter): function that update the 
pattern with the new letter.

- run_single_game(words_list): the function choose one word among a list and
run a single game of hangman

- wrong_letter_check(word, wrong_guess_lst): check if there are a wrong letter
in the word

- filter_words_list(words_list, pattern, wrong_guess_lst): filters a list of
words in accordance to the pattern.

- letter_to_index(letter): Return‬‬ ‫‪the‬‬ ‫‪index‬‬ ‫‪of‬‬ ‫‪the‬‬ ‫‪given‬‬ ‫‪letter‬‬ ‫‪in‬‬ ‫‪an‬‬ ‫‪alphabet‬‬ ‫‪
list.‬‬

- index_to_letter(index) : Return‬‬ ‫‪the‬‬ ‫‪letter‬‬ ‫‪corresponding‬‬ ‫‪to‬‬ ‫‪the‬‬ ‫‪given‬‬ ‫‪index.‬‬

- choose_letter(words_hint, pattern): define who is the letter (not already find)
that is more present in a list of words

- main(): This function allows to run the program.
 
